Revision history for Gtk3-FzfWidget

0.01  2026-03-21
    - Initial release
    - GTK3 widget embedding fzf as a headless fuzzy-search engine
    - HTTP API communication via fzf --listen
    - Single and multi-select modes
    - ANSI color rendering
    - Four built-in themes: normal, dark, solarized-dark, solarized-light
    - Configurable colors, fonts, tab width
    - fzfw command-line launcher
